## `site-region` shortcode

{% site-region region="us" %}
Your site region is `US`, which is why this line appears. The `EU` line in this section should **not** appear.
{% /site-region %}

{% site-region region="eu" %}
Your site region is `EU`, which is why this line appears. The `US` line in this section should **not** appear.
{% /site-region %}

